@startuml SD_12_BrowseSearchEvents
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Duyệt & Tìm kiếm Sự kiện
' FR-12~FR-14: Browse + Search + Filter + Pagination
' ============================================================

title **SD-12: Duyệt & Tìm kiếm Sự kiện\n(Browse + Search + Filter)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
    ParticipantBorderColor #E65100
    ArrowColor #E65100
}

actor "Guest/Attendee" as User #LightGreen
participant "Browser" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "EventListServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #FFF3E0
participant "EventService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "EventDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Trang chủ - Featured Events ==

User -> Browser: Truy cập trang chủ
Browser -> Controller: GET /
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: getFeaturedEvents()
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findFeatured()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT TOP 6 e.*, c.name as cat,\nu.fullName as organizer\nFROM Events e\nJOIN Categories c ON e.categoryId=c.categoryId\nJOIN Users u ON e.organizerId=u.userId\nWHERE e.status='approved'\nAND e.isFeatured=1\nAND e.endDate > GETDATE()\nORDER BY e.startDate
activate DB
DB --> DAO: List<Event>
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: featured events
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: events
deactivate Service

Controller -> Service: getUpcomingEvents(page=1, size=12)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findUpcoming(offset, limit)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT e.*, c.name,\nCOUNT(o.orderId) as orderCount\nFROM Events e ...\nWHERE status='approved'\nAND endDate > GETDATE()\nORDER BY startDate\nOFFSET ? ROWS\nFETCH NEXT ? ROWS ONLY
activate DB
DB --> DAO: List<Event> + totalCount
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: events + total
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: events, pagination
deactivate Service

Controller --> Browser: Forward → index.jsp\n(featured, upcoming, categories)
deactivate Controller
Browser --> User: Homepage: Featured +\nUpcoming events

== Tìm kiếm & Filter ==

User -> Browser: Tìm kiếm "nhạc hội"\n+ Filter: category="Âm nhạc"\n+ Sort: Ngày gần nhất
Browser -> Controller: GET /events?\nq=nhạc hội\n&category=music\n&sort=date_asc\n&page=1
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: Parse query params:\n- searchQuery = "nhạc hội"\n- categorySlug = "music"\n- sortBy = "date_asc"\n- page = 1, pageSize = 12

Controller -> Service: searchEvents(\nsearchQuery, filters, sort, page)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: searchWithFilters(params)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT e.*, c.name, u.fullName,\n(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ...) as totalCount\nFROM Events e\nJOIN Categories c ON ...\nJOIN Users u ON ...\nWHERE e.status = 'approved'\nAND e.endDate > GETDATE()\n**AND (e.title LIKE '%nhạc hội%'**\n**OR e.location LIKE '%nhạc hội%'**\n**OR e.shortDescription LIKE '%nhạc hội%')**\n**AND c.slug = 'music'**\n**ORDER BY e.startDate ASC**\nOFFSET 0 ROWS\nFETCH NEXT 12 ROWS ONLY
activate DB
DB --> DAO: List<Event> + totalCount
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: events (filtered)
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: Build pagination info:\ntotalPages = ceil(total/12)\ncurrentPage = 1\nhasNext = (page < totalPages)

Service --> Controller: SearchResult {\n  events: [...],\n  total: 25,\n  page: 1,\n  totalPages: 3\n}
deactivate Service

Controller -> Service: getAllCategories()
activate Service
Service -> DB: SELECT * FROM Categories\nWHERE isActive=1 ORDER BY name
activate DB
DB --> Service: categories
deactivate DB
Service --> Controller: categories
deactivate Service

Controller --> Browser: Forward → events.jsp\n(events, pagination, categories,\ncurrent filters)
deactivate Controller
Browser --> User: Kết quả tìm kiếm:\n25 sự kiện (trang 1/3)\n+ Active filters sidebar

== Pagination ==

User -> Browser: Click trang 2
Browser -> Controller: GET /events?q=nhạc hội\n&category=music&sort=date_asc\n&page=2
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: searchEvents(..., page=2)
activate Service
Service -> DB: ... OFFSET 12 ROWS\nFETCH NEXT 12 ROWS ONLY
activate DB
DB --> Service: Next 12 events
deactivate DB
Service --> Controller: page 2 results
deactivate Service
Controller --> Browser: Forward → events.jsp (page 2)
deactivate Controller
Browser --> User: Trang 2 kết quả

@enduml
